Full Description: Founded in 2007, Glassbooth is an award-winning nonprofit creating innovative ways to access political information. Glassbooth's first product was glassbooth.org, a site that helped users educate themselves on the issues and decide who to vote for in public elections through a simple, intuitive, and transparent process. In its first year, glassbooth.org had three million organic users, struck syndication deals with CBS and DISH Network, and was featured in The New York Times, Wired, and the CBS Evening News. Glassbooth was an Official Honoree at the 2008 Webby’s and was named the “Best Political Website of 2008” by CNET. In 2010, Glassbooth partnered with Yahoo! to cover UK elections, launched an election quiz in New Zealand, and partnered with local news organizations and non-profits to cover local elections around the U.S. in places like New Orleans and Wisconsin. Glassbooth in Wired: https://web.archive.org/web/20110817213724/http://www.wired.com/politics/onlinerights/news/2008/01/glassbooth On the CBS Evening News: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DPC4ui3TPXo As CNET's top election website of 2008: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pB-Ta1Ily5I On Current TV: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ToG5f1194fk As a 2008 "Webby Award Official Honoree": http://winners.webbyawards.com/2008/web/general-website/politics/honorees

Description: We offer experienced, professional, and personalized legal services. we want to be there to help soothe your fears and get you the best help
Full Description: Criminal Defense: Criminal prosecution is a terrifying experience that you shouldn't face alone. You aren't sure where to start, but you know you want the best representation possible. The Law Office of Les Downs is here to provide you with just that.  We handle all aspects and levels of criminal charges including all levels of felonies, misdemeanors, DUI defense, post-conviction work, trial work, and more. We offer a FREE initial consultation and promise you dedicated and passionate representation. We have a lifelong history of criminal defense and will fight for you!  Family Divorce and Law: When you're going through a divorce or family issue, you want things to be handled as gently and as quickly as possible. At the Law Office of Les Downs, we know what it takes to get you the outcome you’re looking for. No two cases are alike - we understand this and so do you. Your case is specific, and you have specific goals you want to achieve. When you call Attorney Les Downs, he will sit down with you and explain your rights so you understand your options under the law. Whether it's divorce, child custody, or another area of the law, we've got you covered. Trust us to get you the outcome you deserve.  Bankruptcy: If you're having trouble keeping up with your financial responsibilities, you may qualify for Chapter 7 bankruptcy. You can eliminate or reduce your debts, stall foreclosure, or get a mortgage modification. Chapter 7 is the most common form of bankruptcy due to the fact that it relieves common debts such as medical bills or unsecured debts. When you choose the Law Office of Les Downs, we'll help you put your debt behind you so you can focus on your present and future financial needs.
